 * - number of photos enhanced to 65k (was only 256, added 2nd byte to EPROM)
 * - added deepsleep after cam or SD card error (not blocking device from another restarts) 
 * - added watchdog as workaraund for random freezes on SD or cam initialisation
 
  Rui Santos 
  Complete project details at https://RandomNerdTutorials.com/esp32-cam-take-photo-save-microsd-card
  
  IMPORTANT!!! 
   - Select Board "AI Thinker ESP32-CAM"
   - GPIO 0 must be connected to GND to upload a sketch
   - After connecting GPIO 0 to GND, press the ESP32-CAM on-board RESET button to put your board in flashing mode
  
